        <updateDate>2021-06-09T15:59:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Gun Owner Privacy Act</strong></p> <p>This bill restricts the use of federal funds in connection with the implementation and operation of a firearms-related background check system.</p> <p>Specifically, it prohibits the use of federal funds for</p> <ul> <li>a firearms-related background check system that does not immediately destroy all information about a person who is eligible to own firearms, or</li> <li>the implementation or collection of a tax or fee in connection with a firearms-related background check.</li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
